    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is very reliable; the engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are functioning as they should. While there are some minor signs of regular use consistent with its age, the interior remains clean and the exterior paint retains a nice shine. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a solid, honest car.",
